Computer's screen what was going on in High risk lab's area, she took

three airtight doors closed insulate the labs of the base.

Thyphon and Electra were inside the lab with Chameleon and soon they 
fell in stasis lock. Blacknightmare saw all thanks the computer. She 
saw Scorpyo in a lab, Chameleon, Thyphon and electra in area 2, near 
of high risk labs... "I wonder if they're alive" asked her self the 
femme.
